						<div class="postbody">Question A<br />$4015 IF-D NT21<br />$4017 MI-- ----<br />Focus only on $4015.D6 and $4017.D6.<br />1. If $4017.D6 is 0, when read $4015, then $4015.D6 return 0 and $4015.D6 set 1.<br />2. If $4017.D6 is 0, when read $4015, then $4015.D6 return 1 and $4015.D6 set 0.<br />3. If $4017.D6 is 1, when read $4015, then $4015.D6 return 0 and $4015.D6 set 1.<br />4. If $4017.D6 is 1, when read $4015, then $4015.D6 return 1 and $4015.D6 set 0.<br />Which two are right?<br /><br />Question B<br />Assume 4015.D0 is set and $4000.D5(length counter halt) is <strong>set</strong>.<br />Write $4003, whether reload length counter or not?<br />Thanks.</div>

					
